vulnerability_details: Like polar bears who must swim impossible distances between
  shrinking ice floes, Aput's hunting grounds have retreated beyond the reach of his
  traditional methods. The sea ice that once supported his family's 800-year hunting
  tradition now forms too late, breaks too early, and lies too far from shore.
